snippet.title: Project O.R.C.S. | Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Craft unique worlds. 
Tell epic stories.
Embark upon magical quests. 

All with your friends!

Announcing Project O.R.C.S. our brand new CSRPG where you and your friends collaborate to create adventures that are dynamic as your party!

Wishlist us on Steam today! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2332100/Project_ORCS

Like, Subscribe, and Follow us on our other socials for any and all updates Project O.R.C.S.
